message.body: Hey do you still have your phonetics notes?
Yes I do! Just the class notes, I got ridof the book
Nvm! Mine are surprisingly still on blackboard
So we got all the interviewees on Monday night (28th)....except I haven't heard anything from Ali......oh
When did you send out the email about it?
January 10, sent out a Facebook message a few days ago. There's a high possibility she's on vacation =P
Haha ok its fine we'll go on with the others but still wait for her reply
Of course, of course. Should we book the teaching lab 5-7 now, just for safety? (Our last interview would end at 6:15 presently)
Yeah do it!! Ah I'm excited haha
Me too! I feel like we're all gonna have a great semester =)
Still terrified for that artic project hahaha
I work so much better in groups
TERRIFIED. I work better in groups, too! Although you always risk getting a sucky group
True lol and at least its split into 3 parts
Yup yup. We can all also collaborate and help each other out, even if we're not working in a group specifically
